---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Story & Philosophy" description="Learn about Bali Sunny Kids, a nurturing international preschool in Ubud, Bali, providing nature-inspired early childhood education since 2000.">
    <!-- 1. Hero/Intro Section -->
    <section class="relative py-24 px-6 md:px-12 bg-sunny-yellow/10 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 text-sunny-charcoal leading-tight animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-8 duration-700">
                A Sanctuary for <span class="text-sunny-blue">Wonder</span> and Heartfelt Care
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-medium max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Discover a nurturing early childhood education in Gianyar, where children bloom in the magic of childhood, surrounded by the serenity of Bali's rice fields.
            </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Decorative Elements -->
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-32 h-32 bg-sunny-yellow/20 rounded-full -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 blur-2xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-sunny-green/10 rounded-full translate-x-1/3 translate-y-1/3 blur-3xl"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- 2. Our Story -->
    <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
            <div class="relative group">
                <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-sunny-yellow/10 rounded-[3rem] -rotate-2 group-hover:rotate-0 transition-all duration-500"></div>
                <img src="/images/about-philosophy.jpg" alt="Bali Sunny Kids History" class="relative z-10 rounded-[3rem] shadow-2xl w-full object-cover aspect-[4/3]" />
                <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl z-20 hidden md:block border-2 border-sunny-yellow/20">
                    <span class="block text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-sunny-yellow">25+</span>
                    <span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Years of Love</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-sunny-charcoal leading-tight">Rooted in Ubud Since 2000</h2>
                <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
                    <p>
                        In the year 2000, amidst the rustling palm fronds and vibrant greenery of Ubud, Bali Sunny Kids opened its doors with a simple yet profound dream: to create a safe haven where the youngest generation could thrive in harmony with nature and community.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        What began as a small family-like community has blossomed into a cherished destination for international/expat families and local parents seeking a nurturing early childhood education in Bali. Our school is more than just a place of learning; it is a space where every child is deeply seen and their unique rhythm is honored.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        For over two decades, we have remained true to our peaceful Gianyar roots, offering a tropical sunshine-filled environment where children can experience the true magic of childhood before the formal pressures of later schooling begin.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 3. Our Philosophy -->
    <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 bg-sunny-cream relative">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-12 text-sunny-charcoal">The Sunny Philosophy</h2>
            
            <div class="relative mb-16">
                <span class="absolute -top-12 -left-4 text-9xl text-sunny-yellow/20 font-serif leading-none">“</span>
                <blockquote class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-heading font-medium text-gray-700 italic leading-snug px-8 relative z-10">
                    The Universe is one great kindergarten for man. Everything that exists has brought with it its own peculiar lesson.
                </blockquote>
                <p class="mt-4 font-bold text-sunny-blue uppercase tracking-widest">— Friedrich Froebel</p>
            </div>

            <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-left">
                <p>
                    At Bali Sunny Kids, we believe that children are naturally curious, capable, and full of wonder. Our role as educators is not to "fill" them with information, but to provide the fertile soil in which their interests can bloom. 
                </p>
                <p>
                    We embrace a <strong>play-based, nature-inspired preschool</strong> approach that draws from globally respected philosophies like Reggio Emilia. By following the child's lead and providing gentle bilingual exposure (English primary with natural Bahasa Indonesia & Balinese cultural elements), we foster a lifelong love for discovery.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 4. Our Vision (Pillars) -->
    <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">Our Four Core Pillars</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-500">How we nurture your child's journey every day.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all border-t-8 border-sunny-blue flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-sunny-blue/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6">🛡️</div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold mb-4 text-sunny-charcoal">Emotional Safety</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">A low teacher:child ratio (1:6–1:8) ensures every child feels deeply seen, cherished, and emotionally secure.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all border-t-8 border-sunny-yellow flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-sunny-yellow/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6">🤸</div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold mb-4 text-sunny-charcoal">Playful Learning</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Child-led exploration and joyful play-based kindergarten experiences that spark creative problem-solving.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all border-t-8 border-sunny-green flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-sunny-green/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6">🌿</div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold mb-4 text-sunny-charcoal">Nature Connection</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Daily immersion in Bali’s magical nature, teaching sustainability and respect for our tropical environment.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all border-t-8 border-sunny-charcoal flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-sunny-charcoal/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6">🏘️</div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold mb-4 text-sunny-charcoal">Family Community</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">A small, family-like community feel with strong parent partnerships and heart-centered communication.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 5. Our Educators -->
    <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 bg-sunny-blue/5">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
                <div class="lg:w-1/2">
                    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 text-sunny-charcoal leading-tight">Guided by Heart, Trained for Excellence</h2>
                    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                        Our teachers are more than educators; they are caring guides who follow children's interests rather than forcing rigid academics. 
                    </p>
                    <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
                        <p>Every member of our team is chosen for their passionate dedication to early childhood and their ability to create a "home away from home" for your little ones.</p>
                        <p>We prioritize ongoing training in the latest play-based methodologies and bilingual pedagogy (English and Bahasa Indonesia), ensuring a high standard of care that meets international benchmarks while remaining authentically Balinese.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="lg:w-1/2 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <!-- Insert team photo grid here -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-[2rem] shadow-lg">
                        <div class="aspect-square bg-gray-100 rounded-[1.5rem] mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-300">Bio Photo</div>
                        <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-sunny-charcoal">Our Lead Guides</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-sunny-blue font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Passionate & Qualified</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-[2rem] shadow-lg md:translate-y-8">
                        <div class="aspect-square bg-gray-100 rounded-[1.5rem] mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-300">Bio Photo</div>
                        <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-sunny-charcoal">Supporting Hearts</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-sunny-blue font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Caring & Bilingual</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 6. Why Families Choose Us -->
    <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">Why Families Call Us Home</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-500">The Bali Sunny Kids difference at a glance.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <ul class="space-y-6">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-sunny-yellow/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-sunny-yellow text-sm">✓</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium"><strong>Rice-field serenity:</strong> A peaceful, safe location away from busy roads.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-sunny-blue/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-sunny-blue text-sm">✓</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium"><strong>Bilingual exposure:</strong> English-primary with natural integration of Bahasa Indonesia.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-sunny-green/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-sunny-green text-sm">✓</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium"><strong>Low ratios:</strong> Personalized attention (1:6–1:8) for emotional security.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-sunny-yellow/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-sunny-yellow text-sm">✓</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium"><strong>Balanced nutrition:</strong> Healthy, local, and mindful meals shared family-style.</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="space-y-6">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-sunny-blue/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-sunny-blue text-sm">✓</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium"><strong>Legacy of trust:</strong> Serving the Ubud expat and local community since 2000.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-sunny-green/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-sunny-green text-sm">✓</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium"><strong>Holistic development:</strong> Focusing on confidence, creativity, and wellbeing.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-sunny-yellow/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-sunny-yellow text-sm">✓</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium"><strong>Cultural respect:</strong> Gentle introduction to Balinese arts, songs, and traditions.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-sunny-blue/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-sunny-blue text-sm">✓</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium"><strong>Sustainability:</strong> Hands-on nature play that builds a respect for our earth.</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 7. CTA / Welcome Section -->
    <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 text-center bg-sunny-blue text-white overflow-hidden relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-20 pointer-events-none">
            <img src="/images/enrollment-hero.jpg" class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="Background" />
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto relative z-10">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-heading font-bold mb-8">We can't wait to <span class="text-sunny-yellow">meet you</span></h2>
            <p class="text-xl mb-12 text-blue-50 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                Choosing a school is a journey of the heart. We invite you to visit our sanctuary in Ubud, meet our team, and see our children in their joyful exploration.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
                <a href="/enrollment" class="bg-sunny-yellow text-sunny-charcoal px-10 py-4 rounded-full text-xl font-bold hover:scale-110 transition-transform w-full sm:w-auto">Enroll Now</a>
                <a href="/contact" class="bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-md border-2 border-white/50 px-10 py-4 rounded-full text-xl font-bold hover:bg-white/30 transition-all w-full sm:w-auto">Book a Visit</a>
                <a href="https://wa.me/6282255227558" class="text-white font-bold hover:underline underline-offset-8">WhatsApp Chat →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Integration Notes (for reference) -->
    <!-- 
      - Images: Use high-quality photos of children in natural light.
      - Team: Replace placeholders with real staff names and brief heart-centered bios.
      - SEO: Target "international preschool Ubud Bali" and "play-based kindergarten Bali".
    -->
</Layout>
